DESCRIPTION:Interbay summer camps are 3 hours of Serious Fun for kiddos 3-1
	0 years of age! Camp consists of 2 hours of gym time\\\, and 1 hour of sna
	cks and craft time. Every week brings a new and exciting theme for your ca
	mper and we always have blocks\\\, books and coloring pages on standby for
	 those campers that need a break. Camps are held Monday-Wednesday from 1-4
	pm. We offer special discounted pricing for members and camp pack purchase
	s. Non member pricing is $75 for a single camp pass. More information on p
	ack pricing can be found via our scannable QR code. Priority registration 
